data.meta_description:
108 likes, 2 comments - sevasahayog on May 11, 2024: "#SATURDAY_SEVA{128}

"School Kit"- A DREAM COMES TRUE for thousands of  children...

Seva Sahayog Foundation's first school kit assembly of 2024 was successfully held at Thane on 5th May. 

2223  kits assembled with the help of 170 + energetic volunteers & handed over to 27+ beneficiary schools at the assembly venue.

Welcome to join this exciting सेवायज्ञ & experience  joy of sharing. Our next assembly is at  Dadar on 26th May.

School Kit Assembly Location:- 
https://maps.app.goo.gl/cdE7fyqt2PVYdcPJ9

For Donation purpose click on the below:- 
https://rzp.io/l/SK2024".
